h path\\n\\n* chore: move announcements.json and clean up unnecessary files\\n\\n* fix: refactor _run_job to unify session lifecycle and prevent leaks\\n\\n* chore: increase DB connection pool size for non-SQLite databases\\n\\n* fix: add executor shutdown to lifespan to prevent semaphore/resource leakage\\n\\n* chore: update announcements for V0.5.0 launch\\n\\n* chore: focus announcement on stability fixes\\n\\n* chore: correct versioning to v0.4.4 and restore v0.4.3 history\\n\\n* chore: fully restore changelog history and sync announcements to v0.4.4\\n\\n* chore: remove non-essential files from Docker image to keep it slim\\n\\n 17 Mar 06:47\\n\\n 16 Mar 13:39\\n\\n 15 Mar 09:47\\n\\n## What's Changed\\n\\n- chore(deps): bump aiohttp from 3.12.13 to 3.13.3 in the uv group across 1 directory by [@dependabot](https://github.com/dependabot)[bot] in [#16](https://github.com/KylinMountain/TradingAgents-AShare/pull/16)\\n\\n- chore(deps): bump orjson from 3.10.18 to 3.11.6 in the uv group across 1 directory by [@dependabot](https://github.com/dependabot)[bot] in [#15](https://github.com/KylinMountain/TradingAgents-AShare/pull/15)\\n\\n- chore(deps): bump langchain-core from 0.3.83 to 1.2.11 in the uv group across 1 directory by [@dependabot](https://github.com/dependabot)[bot] in [#13](https://github.com/KylinMountain/TradingAgents-AShare/pull/13)\\n\\n- chore(deps): bump langgraph-checkpoint from 2.0.26 to 4.0.0 in the uv group across 1 directory by [@dependabot](https://github.com/dependabot)[bot] in [#14](https://github.com/KylinMountain/TradingAgents-AShare/pull/14)\\n\\n- chore(deps): bump protobuf from 5.29.5 to 5.29.6 in the uv group across 1 directory by [@dependabot](https://github.com/dependabot)[bot] in [#11](https://github.com/KylinMountain/TradingAgents-AShare/pull/11)\\n\\n- chore(deps): bump urllib3 from 2.4.0 to 2.6.3 in the uv group across 1 directory by [@dependabot](https://github.com/dependabot)[bot] in [#10](https://github.com/KylinMountain/Tradi