{"type":"message","id":"7ad98876","parentId":"8ce60836","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:17:57.614Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The subagent has completed successfully. It has created 7 new analyst modules, bringing the total to 15+ analysts. Now I need to test if the new version works. Let me generate a new token and test the analysis.","thinkingSignature":"e7dbaa967c560ce1cabf0ef9447c971d3eef792a60160ec2550997e201f96c6f"},{"type":"text","text":"## εΦÄεèëε°¨φàêοΦ¹πüéâ\n\nε≠êδΜΘγêÜφàêεäüεà¦εΜΚδΚÜ **7 δΗΣφ•ΑεàÜφûêεΗàφ®Γεù½**οΦö\n\n| # | εàÜφûêεΗà | εäüηÉΫ |\n|---|--------|------|\n| 1 | industry_analyst | ηΓ¨δΗöηΕ΄εäΩεàÜφûê |\n| 2 | valuation_analyst | δΦΑεÄΦεàÜφûê (DCF, PE, PB) |\n| 3 | financial_quality_analyst | η¥ΔεäΓη¥®ι΅èεàÜφûê |\n| 4 | management_analyst | γ°ΓγêÜε±²η·³δΦΑ |\n| 5 | risk_analyst | ιΘéιô©ε¦†γ¥†εàÜφûê |\n| 6 | institutional_analyst | φ€Κφû³φ¨¹δΜ™εàÜφûê |\n| 7 | flows_analyst | ηΒ³ι΅ëφΒ¹εêëεàÜφûê |\n\n**φÄΜη°ΓοΦö15 δΫçεàÜφûêεΗà + game_theory**\n\n---\n\nγéΑε€®φΒ΄η·ïφ•Αγâàφ€§οΦö\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rwaz2sijcu7f_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport requests\n\nemail = 'admin@local.com'\nr1 = requests.post('http://localhost:8000/v1/auth/request-code', json={'email': email})\ndev_code = r1.json().get('dev_code')\n\nr2 = requests.post('http://localhost:8000/v1/auth/verify-code', json={'email': email, 'code': dev_code})\njwt = r2.json().get('access_token')\n\nr3 = requests.post('http://localhost:8000/v1/tokens', headers={'Authorization': f'Bearer {jwt}'}, json={'name': 'test'})\ntoken = r3.json().get('token')\nprint('Token:', token[:30])\n\n# Test with more analysts\nr4 = requests.post('http://localhost:8000/v1/analyze', \n    headers={'Authorization': f'Bearer {token}', 'Content-Type': 'application/json'}, \n    json={'symbol': 'η¥ùηΨΨηç·δΗö'})\nprint('Status:', r4.status_code, r4.text[:100])\n\"","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model"